      <title>Re: Promotional offer, no fine print, so i wrote some for everyone</title>
      <link>http://eqforums.station.sony.com/eq/board/message?board.id=SOE&amp;message.id=3982#M3982</link>
      <description>If you have complaints regarding the quality of service you have received, we ask that you email eqcs@soe.sony.com with the details of the complaint and the ticket number of the petition you submitted regarding the original issue. This email address is not intended as an alternative method to the in-game petition system and should only be used for complaints regarding quality of service.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;The eqcs@soe.sony.com email address can also be used to offer feedback and suggestions regarding ways to improve the ticketing system. Feedback and suggestion emails, while important to SOE and often quite useful, will most likely not receive a response.</description>
